  "title": "DevOps Engineer",
  "description": "<p>We’re looking for a DevOps Engineer to help our client to integrate their developments and operations.</p><p>DevOps Engineer/ SRE</p><p>Responsibilities</p><ul><li>Develop and maintain full stack web application backend and frontend</li><li>Implement CICD pipeline to streamline development and release processes</li><li>Integrate tools such as version control system build automation tool testing framework and development tools into the software development lifecycle</li><li>Troubleshoot and resolve issues related to tool integration</li><li>Familiarity with cloud services and infrastructure management</li><li>Design and implement secure automation solutions</li><li>Maintain or setup monitoring tools notifications and analytics</li><li>Maintain version control systems and configuration management tools</li><li>Lead the design and implementation and maintenance of RedHat Linux environments</li><li>Experience in automation scripts and use of Ansible for system configuration and orchestrations</li><li>Provide virtualization and containerization solution using VMware and RedHat OpenShift</li><li>Expert in support and troubleshooting for critical system issues</li><li>Coordinate with development team and architects to facilitate continuous integration and delivery pipeline</li><li>Adhere to industry standards and best practices</li></ul><p>Qualification</p><ul><li>Worked on Linux platform</li><li>Experienced as full stack developer with strong background in tool integration</li><li>Experienced on programming languages and frameworks such as HTMLCCS JavaScript Java Python Nodejs Angular etc.</li><li>Familiarity with database MYSQL MongoDB,webserversApache and UIUX design</li><li>Handson experience of Ansible for automation and configuration management</li><li>Experienced with OpenShift for container orchestration and management</li><li>Experience in VMware infrastructure and its integration with physical and cloud environments</li><li>Knowledge on scripting such as shell</li><li>Problem solving ability</li><li>Relevant certification</li></ul>",
